## 18. Post-Deployment Common Failures

| Symptom | Likely Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------------|-----|
| Component not in View Designer palette | Missing from `index.ts` export or main module imports | Add export and import, rebuild and redeploy |
| Component in palette but drag fails | Registration module constructor error | Check browser console; fix registration code |
| `ɵmod undefined` error in console | AOT compilation didn't process the registration module | Check Module naming, static metadata in decorators, registration wiring (Section 13) |
| Design preview blank | Design component template error or missing `standalone: true` | Check design `.html` and component decorator |
| Property inspector empty | `setInspectorConfig` not called or returns malformed config | Verify design model constructor calls `sandbox.updateInspectorConfig(...)` |
| Runtime shows blank box | Runtime component throws on init | Check browser console; verify `super.ngOnInit()` is called |
| "Set Property" action has no effect | `setProperty` missing case or missing `notifyPropertyChanged` | Add case in switch, ensure `notifyPropertyChanged` is called |
| Component not in expression builder | `setCommonDataDictionary` not called in design model | Add data dictionary setup in design model constructor |
| 405 Method Not Allowed on API call | Using GET instead of POST for DataPage | Switch to `POST /api/rx/application/datapage` |
| Component shows after deploy but old version | Browser cache serving stale bundle | Hard refresh + logout/login |
| View save fails with validation error | `validateStandardProps` not called or custom validation too strict | Check `validate` method in design model |
| Component in manifest JSON but not in View Designer | Component type in `com-mycompany-sample-app.json` but missing from compiled JS chunks | Docker bind mount stale sync — `index.ts` or main module edits didn't propagate to container. Verify with `grep` on the built JS, then apply edits directly inside the container via `docker exec` and rebuild. See Section 15 and Section 16 "Compiled JS Bundle Verification". |
| Template parse error: `Incomplete block` | Unescaped `@` character in HTML template (e.g., email addresses) | Replace `@` with `&#64;` in template HTML |
| API returns ERROR 12095 | DateTime field uses ISO 8601 instead of epoch millis | See Java Build & Deploy checklist — AR System Platform Quirks |
| API returns ERROR 307 on record create | Required field missing (usually Status/Description) or attachment before record | Set field 7 (Status) and field 8 (Description) explicitly |
| Processing stuck at 0% | Relying on Rules to fire repeatedly for batch processing | Rules fire once per event — inline the processing loop in the service |

